	<main> 
		<div class="container" id="main-content">

		<h1>Permanent Impairment Compensation</h1>
		
		<div class="form-group">

			<div class="breakout clearfix">
				<p>If you have been left with ongoing impairment you may be entitled to a compensation payment. We call this <a href="https://www.dva.gov.au/factsheet-mrc07-permanent-impairment-compensation-payments" rel="external" target="_black"><strong>permanent&nbsp;impairment&nbsp;compensation</strong></a>. You may be eligible if:</p>
					<ul style="margin-bottom:20px;">
						<li>after treatment you still have an impairment or lifestyle rescriction,</li>
						<li>the impairment or restriction is likely to continue indefinitely, and</li>
						<li>your condition has stabilised.</li>
				</ul></p>
				<p>The application process invloves one or multiple medical assessments to determine the level of impairment or lifestyle restriction.</p>
			</div>

			<fieldset>
				<legend class="legend-label">Would you like to apply for permanent impairment compensation?</legend>
				<div class="radio-toggle">
					<label class="on label-left" for="pi-yes"><input id="pi-yes" type="radio" name="pi"><span>Yes</span></label>
					<label class="off label-right" for="pi-no"><input id="pi-no" type="radio" name="pi"><span>Not now</span></label>
				</div>

				<div class="form-group pi-yes" style="display:none;">
					<p>We will get in touch with you about the next steps.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="form-group pi-no" style="display:none;">
					<p>You can come back at any time to apply for permanent impairment compensation.</p>
				</div>

			</fieldset>

		</div>
	
		
		
		
		<div class="pagination">
		  <button class="uikit-btn uikit-btn--tertiary" onclick="window.location.href = '/needs1'">Previous</button>
		  <button class="uikit-btn uikit-btn--tertiary" onclick="window.location.href = '#open-modal'">Cancel</button>
		  <button class="uikit-btn floated" onclick="window.location.href = '/needs3'">Next</button>
		</div>
		
		<% include claim/partials/cancel-modal.ejs %>
		
		</div>
	</main>
   
	<% include ../global/partials/footer.ejs %>
